      <title>华尔街押注特朗普将为市场带来新财富</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/wall-street-bets-on-new-riches-ahead-in-markets-all-in-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年以来，大量华尔街专业人士一直在质疑无差别风险反弹的持久性，这种反弹已导致股价上涨数万亿美元、比特币飙升、信贷热潮等。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/wall-street-bets-on-new-riches-ahead-in-markets-all-in-on-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 21:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
